{
  "texts": [
    "To dig deeper into the subject matter, we need to ask the following questions: Why is this happening?",
    "Why does this keep happening through the ages?",
    "Why do we develop these animistic tendencies toward new technologies?",
    "The answers lie in the longstanding habit of human users to 'project agency, feelings and creativity onto machines' [45 p.2].",
    "This is animism in action, whereby an inanimate technology, nowadays AI, is perceived as an agentic entity."
  ]
}